{
  "name": "RPlog_Comfort_Among_Beasts",
  "title": "Comfort Among Beasts",
  "summary": "Aboard an Imperial station, the smuggler Captain Morganna delivers Fleet Admiral Adlerson's daughter and braces for another cutting encounter with the shadow-cloaked Captain Atrox, trading acid-laced barbs while demanding her ship be refueled. Station business swirls around them, a yellow alert, the arrest of a CSA trader named Mekeal, and the silent observation of Adlerson, but Atrox quietly orders the Sable Fox fueled and steers the conversation toward the two of them. Beneath their mutual cruelty, the hardened pair confront something neither knows how to name: a raw, terrifying tenderness. They circle each other through tears, fear, and confusion, admitting they think of one another constantly, before regaining their sadistic composure, parting as the bonded predators they are with a promise to meet again.",
